    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just feels like a trap, you know? like everyone is just playing house in a house that's already on fire. when you say \"letting go of the burden,\" do you mean just giving up on trying to fix things, or do you mean something more permanent? like, is it actually a rational way to deal with the stress of it all?",
